snippet.textDisplay:
This song is superb. This version and the studio version too. It's raw, it's pure, even without lyrics translated it makes me feel things. It's inspiring, it's melancholic and even a bit eerie. But it's powerful. And it's because of how they (and the team that works with them) put their passion, their artistry, their love into what they do. BigHit really gives us Artist and Music for healing. And if the music is amazing, the lyrics just hit you right in the centre of your heart.
Thank you, BTS. For making music. For making art. I hope that you keep doing it for as long as you wish and I'll keep supporting you. And when you decide you no longer want to, I'll support you even then, because you changed me, you changed my life and you contribute to my happiness.

بعد التحليل بعتقد هي رسالة بطس النا بتمنى تقرأوها عشان مايتعذبو بطس هني وعم يوصلوا الرسالة النا بتمنى تتمعنو بكلامهم مكتوبة عربي وانجليزي ...read please I guess this is their message to us
Each of us has two characters, a peaceful person and an evil person. Outside, you appear as an angel, but inside there is a black swan. The white character is looking for perfection. The black character is looking for control. Without evil, injustice or bullying, you will not become stronger. You can control the darkness inside you and live freely despite all the difficult circumstances that you went through. Do not give in. Be strong and learn from your failure.
كل واحد منا لديه شخصيتين ، شخص مسالم وشخص شرير. في الخارج ، تظهر كملاك ، ولكن في الداخل هناك بجعة سوداء. الشخصية البيضاء تبحث عن الكمال. الشخصية السوداء تبحث عن السيطرة. بدون الشر أو الظلم أو التسلط ، لن تصبح أقوى. يمكنك التحكم في الظلام بداخلك والعيش بحرية رغم كل الظروف الصعبة التي مرت بها. لا تستسلم. كن قوياً وتعلم من إخفاقك....arab army:)
